page.title: 142 PRIMARY SC.PUPILS B/BRIGGS
page.content:
MY NAME IS{HEATHER GIBSON.}I LIKE LISTENING TO POP MUSIC. MY HOBBIES ARE SWIMMING, RUNNING, AND DANCING. I GO SWIMMING 5 DAYS A WEEK. I GO TO GALAS MOST WEEKENDS. I GO DANCING ON SATURDAY MORNINGS. MY FAVOURITE POP GROUP IS 'U2'
MY NAME IS{JILL BRASH.}I LIKE READING. I'VE READ THE 'NANCY DREW' SERIES AND THE 'JILL ROBINSON' SERIES JUST NOW. POP IS MY FAVOURITE MUSIC, AND 'WHAM!' IS MY FAVOURITE GROUP. I LIKE WATCHING 'DALLAS','DYNASTY', AND 'AUF WIEDERSEHEN, PET'. I GET A COMIC 'NICKY' ONCE A WEEK.
